Summary

HTML: Defines the structure and content of the webpage.

CSS: Enhances the appearance and layout of the page.

JavaScript: Adds functionality for user interaction (e.g., checking AQI).

JSON: Stores data for future integration with JavaScript to dynamically provide AQI information.